Financial Corporation ofAmerica's American Savings and Loan Association unit said itsigned a definitive agreement to buy three retail savingsbranches from Gibraltar Financial Corp's &lt;GFC> GibraltarSavings unit.    The purchase, which must be approved by the Federal HomeLoan Bank and the California Department of Savings and Loans,would increase American Savings' deposits by about 40 mln dlrs.    The branches are in La Jolla, La Mesa and San JuanCapistrano, Calif. Reuter&#3;